OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to former village
OL,4,Cpost lady who died at Ashton near
OL,5,CHelston
OL,7,FA woman who died in the small village
OL,8,Fof Ashton near Helston in Cornwall on
OL,9,FFriday 29 May has been named as Jenny
OL,10,FFirth, 81, who served the village as
OL,11,Fthe post lady for more than 25 years.
OL,13,FMs Firth's family have paid tribute
OL,14,Fsaying: "Our family is utterly
OL,15,Fdevastated by the sudden and tragic
OL,16,Floss of our beautiful mum and granny.
OL,26,@vD@IOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
