PN,43802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1780992973
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to former village
OL,4,Cpost lady who died at Ashton near
OL,5,CHelston
OL,7,F"She was an incredibly fun-loving,
OL,8,Fmischievous and charismatic lady who
OL,9,Fbrought great joy into the lives of
OL,10,Feveryone who knew her. Jenny dedicated
OL,11,Fherself to her family and her
OL,12,Fcommunity.
OL,14,F"Jenny loved Cornwall, her home, her
OL,15,Fgarden and Ashton village where she
OL,16,Fhad lived for more than 60 years, and
OL,17,Fthe village in turn loved her back.
OL,18,FHer death has had a profound and far-
OL,19,Freaching impact on an entire community.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1780992973
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to former village
OL,4,Cpost lady who died at Ashton near
OL,5,CHelston
OL,7,F"We refuse to let her death overshadow
OL,8,Fthe beautiful life she lived. We are
OL,9,Ffully determined to focus on her
OL,10,Flegacy and honour her through a
OL,11,Flifetime of joyful, positive memories.
OL,13,F"She was an elderly and vulnerable
OL,14,Flady, and we are utterly heartbroken
OL,15,Fby her death.
OL,17,FEdward Holden, 36, of Alexandra Place,
OL,18,FPenzance, appeared at Truro Crown
OL,19,FCourt on Tuesday 2 June charged with
OL,20,Frape and murder.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
